  Text: |-
    Not suitable as pets
    
    Can withstand wide swings in water quality and forage effectively in low visibility
    
    Swims: bottom
    
    Highly specialized respiratory system
    Sedentary, secretive, and cover-oriented; emerges more in low light
    
    The South American lungfish is eaten locally.
